👊 UAE kicks out Israeli diplomat after alleged bar shenanigans with women

Israel has recalled its ambassador to the UAE following reports of the diplomat’s unbecoming conduct, if local media is to be believed.

This is what ostensibly occurred:

♦️ Several months ago on a Friday night, Israel’s Ambassador to the UAE Yossi Shelley visited a bar in Abu Dhabi while in the company of several friends;

♦️ Details of what exactly took place in the bar are sketchy, but the ambassador’s conduct there was apparently “undignified” according to Emirati standards, with Israel's Channel 12 reporting that sources familiar with the matter said Shelley “crossed the boundaries of personal space”, presumably with his female companions;

♦️ Upon learning of this incident, the Emirati government was quick to notify Israel of how displeased it was;

♦️ “Shelley’s behavior was not acceptable and even harms our honor,” the UAE reportedly told Israel.

